comentario: Two years ago, I had to distance myself from the girl I wanted to share my life with forever. Sometimes I still remember her in the little things she left behind in my life — especially in the music we used to listen to. She used to play “I Don’t Wanna Be You Anymore” every time we were together. This is the first time I’ve listened to the song all the way through; I’m sure it would’ve been one of our favorites.
